cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CY

This paper deals with automated fact-checking using deep learning techniques, which falls under the category of natural language processing (NLP) and artificial intelligence (AI). Therefore, cs.CL and cs.AI are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also proposes a neural network model, which involves training and optimization, making cs.LG a likely sub-category as well. The paper also deals with information retrieval (IR) and cybernetics (CY) in terms of aggregating signals from external evidence articles and assessing the trustworthiness of their sources. Therefore, cs.IR and cs.CY are also likely sub-categories.
